{"tid":2079131,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[逆權紀錄]反送中一周年 戰線記錄 7.1 發布","createTime":"2020-06-25T14:41:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-25T15:04:00.000Z","uid":361535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"03a592205ae940e9d1ecb2b2efa0ea510d29a5a6","tid":2079131,"uid":361535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T14:41:23.000Z","msg":"從6.12 到6.12，香港人已經經歷咗365日嘅抗爭。希望藉住呢個機會用<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">戰線地圖</span></span></strong>嘅形式去紀錄呢一年香港人嘅血與淚，所以特登整咗個戰線紀錄短片俾大家。下面就有得睇住預告片先&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/mzof6c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Fmzof6c&d=b6PV2mHT5tDC6%2Fq4CXK2StqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=277eb0f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/mzof6c</a><br />\n<br />\n成條片會喺<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">7月1日</span></span>發布，歡迎大家俾啲意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個係逆權戰線紀錄嘅第一部份，之後可能會推出重要日子嘅詳細戰線短片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d657c188879882b37a49498778a2e5abe38508c2","tid":2079131,"uid":361535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T15:04:00.000Z","msg":"推"}]}